---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Freight Brokerage Services | UAT Solutions"
  description="Optimizing logistics and transportation for seamless goods movement across North America. FTL, LTL, and temperature-controlled freight solutions."
>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <section class="bg-dark pt-20 pb-32 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[160%] h-24 md:h-36 bg-cream hero-arch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="text-cream/50 text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-medium">What We Offer</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-cream mt-4 leading-tight">
        Freight <em class="italic font-normal">Services</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-base lg:text-lg mt-6 leading-relaxed">
        Optimizing logistics and transportation for seamless goods movement across North America.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value props bar -->
  <section class="bg-cream-2 border-b border-dark/10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 divide-y md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x divide-dark/10">
      {[
        {
          title: 'Personalized Freight Solutions',
          desc: 'Tailored services to meet your unique logistics and transportation needs efficiently.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Cost Efficiency Focus',
          desc: 'Reducing empty miles to enhance your supply chain\'s cost-effectiveness and reliability.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Reliable Partnerships',
          desc: 'Building long-lasting relationships with businesses for dependable logistics solutions.',
        },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="py-8 px-6 lg:px-10">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-mid text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FTL -->
  <section id="ftl" class="bg-cream py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-dark-2">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601584115197-04ecc0da31d7?w=900&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
            alt="Full truckload freight on highway"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-full h-full border border-accent -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="bg-accent text-light text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase px-3 py-1">Full Truckload</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-dark mt-5 mb-5 leading-tight">
          FTL <em class="italic font-normal">Shipping</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-mid leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Dedicated capacity for time-sensitive loads. When your shipment fills an entire truck,
          FTL is the fastest and most direct option — and UAT Solutions makes it simple.
        </p>
        <p class="text-mid leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Our nationwide carrier network ensures competitive rates with proactive updates
          and a dedicated account manager from first call to final delivery.
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-10">
          {['Nationwide coverage across Canada & the US', 'Competitive, transparent pricing', 'Real-time shipment tracking', 'Dry van, flatbed, and reefer options', 'Dedicated account management'].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-dark">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-light font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors">
          Get an FTL Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LTL -->
  <section id="ltl" class="bg-cream-2 py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <span class="bg-dark text-cream text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase px-3 py-1">Less-Than-Truckload</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-dark mt-5 mb-5 leading-tight">
          LTL <em class="italic font-normal">Freight</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-mid leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Not every shipment fills a full truck — and you shouldn't pay as if it does.
          LTL shipping lets you share trailer space with other shippers, paying only for what you use.
        </p>
        <p class="text-mid leading-relaxed mb-8">
          UAT Solutions optimizes your LTL routes through our established carrier network,
          ensuring competitive pricing and real-time shipment visibility for every pallet.
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-10">
          {['Pay only for the space you use', 'Optimized routing for faster transit', 'Real-time shipment visibility', 'Flexible pickup scheduling', 'Ideal for 1–8 pallets'].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-dark">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-dark hover:bg-dark-2 text-cream font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors">
          Get an LTL Quote
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-dark-2">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586528116311-ad8dd3c8310d?w=900&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
            alt="Logistics warehouse with pallets"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-full h-full border border-dark -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reefer -->
  <section id="reefer" class="bg-cream py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-dark-2">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545987796-200677ee1011?w=900&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
            alt="Temperature controlled freight transport"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-full h-full border border-accent -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="bg-accent text-light text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase px-3 py-1">Temperature-Controlled</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-dark mt-5 mb-5 leading-tight">
          Reefer <em class="italic font-normal">Transport</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-mid leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Sensitive cargo demands careful handling. Our temperature-controlled freight network
          ensures perishable goods — food, pharmaceuticals, chemicals — arrive in perfect condition.
        </p>
        <p class="text-mid leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We work with rigorously vetted reefer carriers who maintain continuous temperature
          monitoring and compliance with all food safety regulations.
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-10">
          {['Continuous temperature monitoring', 'Food-grade and pharmaceutical-grade options', 'Full compliance with food safety regulations', 'Canada-wide and cross-border capable', 'Backup cooling on all long hauls'].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-dark">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-light font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors">
          Get a Reefer Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Carrier section -->
  <section id="carriers" class="bg-dark py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="text-accent text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-semibold">For Carriers</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cream mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Partner <em class="italic font-normal">with us</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Are you a carrier looking for consistent, quality loads? UAT Solutions builds long-term
          partnerships with reliable carriers across Canada and the United States.
        </p>
        <p class="text-cream/70 leading-relaxed mb-10">
          We offer fair rates, fast payment, and a dedicated team that treats you as a partner —
          not just a truck number. Join our growing network today.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-cream hover:bg-cream-2 text-dark font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors inline-block">
          Become a Carrier Partner
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          { num: 'Fast',  label: 'Payment processing' },
          { num: 'Fair',  label: 'Negotiated rates' },
          { num: '24/7',  label: 'Dispatcher support' },
          { num: 'Real',  label: 'Human relationships' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-dark-2 p-6 border border-white/5">
            <p class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-cream">{item.num}</p>
            <p class="text-cream/40 text-xs tracking-wide mt-1">{item.label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="bg-accent py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-light mb-4 leading-tight">
        Let's move your freight.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-light/80 mb-8">Contact us today for a free, no-obligation quote.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-light hover:bg-cream text-accent font-bold px-9 py-4 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors">
        Get a Free Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
